{"tid":194258,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【IT佬悲歌】滙豐合約員工少28日大假 仲要分開食飯","createTime":"2017-04-10T00:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T04:00:18.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c08ce803acca3cf72b11ccce0536209ebfbed5e7","tid":194258,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/080309_632cc50dfa9a5a862582de2557120a53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F080309_632cc50dfa9a5a862582de2557120a53.jpg&h=a3c58a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長工與合約員工「親疏有別」，合約員工除了被裁後沒有「肥雞餐」，僱員福利亦或差天共地。Samuel（化名）指，平日合約員工未能進入長工專用的樓層進膳，但工作量仍是做足7日24小時。<br />\n<br />\nSamuel於滙豐IT部主要負責產品開發，過往參與不少大Project，包括滙豐2月份大力推廣的P2P 手機過數應用程式PayMe。雖然不是長工，但Samuel指平日工作「基本上都係7乘24（做足7日24小時）」，大假方面卻只得7日，反觀長工大假多達35日。<br />\n<br />\n「你話人工我就唔敢講係咪會差過長工，但福利就差好多，好似食飯咁，office有一層只係開放俾長工，合約員工係無得入。」他又指，長工同事差不多近半已加入滙豐10年以上，而他任職的部門近年已沒再聘請長工，僅不斷聘用合約員工，並外判工序予印度等地。<br />\n<br />\n「雖然外地員工人工平，但如果將大部分工序外判，對銀行服務點係會有少部份影響。」Samuel坦言，以往與印度等地的員工合作，溝通上有不少困難，「好似印度、英國就有時差問題，內地員工睇法就好多時同香港人有分歧。」香港人尤以效率高見稱，以1日便可完成的工作為例，Samuel直言「印度要拖成2至3星期，好多時只係因為佢地無check跟進email，就停手唔做。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56543744&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56543744%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170410&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2BynzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=48a5dc86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56543744%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170410&h=89eb82fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56543744&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170410</a>"},{"pid":"09547d00859dc55287bd29b473df120e33ea86fc","tid":194258,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:05:05.000Z","msg":"香港老細對IT賤過地底黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1b58b02634b9abc87c9e75e08550db74e4311b","tid":194258,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1706af9a4604b375581ffc832e4f1a925072d3d8","tid":194258,"uid":64047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:42:52.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲入hsbc做it, 佢請長工都blacklist"},{"pid":"423b920d114f09f801adb5f1906fd336c26084f7","tid":194258,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今時今日仲入hsbc做it, 佢請長工都blacklist</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一炒賠三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個fd做左兩年想轉工<br />\n但今次無比人炒有d唔開心"},{"pid":"f6d6dee30be797c96b559199ad5135217c8d6249","tid":194258,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:09:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ff73834c013e5ba33a6c42817f33e44f0683b485","tid":194258,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:10:26.000Z","msg":"人工包左"},{"pid":"65e31ca1ab6a27479bee3d019d3c252215ed2a22","tid":194258,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌講到好似逼鳩你咁<br />\n入之前就知係合約嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nit狗正一垃圾</blockquote><br />\n仲要做左三年幾 自己攞黎"},{"pid":"8f2c584ce9c068d76cf46414793c486668c23906","tid":194258,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今時今日仲入hsbc做it, 佢請長工都blacklist</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一炒賠三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個fd做左兩年想轉工<br />\n但今次無比人炒有d唔開心</blockquote><br />\n下次跟足勞工法㤡，死未<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25476e5b394956321ef9f3b7ebdd4dac5469047","tid":194258,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:15:51.000Z","msg":"講起印度佬<br />\n滙豐之前會叫現職教印度佬做教完兜撚左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f84fad7f5405a1cdb9b52c0d0c99ea38bd6d5a1","tid":194258,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:00:18.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}